## Usage

### CLI

```bash
# Show available commands
uv run {{ project_name_lower }} --help

# Run specific command
uv run {{ project_name_lower }} [command] [options]
```

### Dashboard (if available)

```bash
uv run streamlit run src/interfaces/dashboard/app.py
```

